'''安·哈特·庫爾特'''（Ann Hart Coulter，{{bd|1961年|12月8日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位右翼<ref>{{cite web |last1=Rosenberg |first1=Eli |title=Ann Coulter once called Trump a 'god.' Now she says he's 'gutless' if he can't build the wall. |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2018/12/21/ann-coulter-once-called-trump-god-now-she-says-hes-gutless-if-he-cant-build-wall/ |website=The Washington Post |accessdate=2019-02-16 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217020239/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2018/12/21/ann-coulter-once-called-trump-god-now-she-says-hes-gutless-if-he-cant-build-wall/ |archive-date=2019-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Sollenberger |first1=Roger |title=Ann Coulter, of All People, Just Handed Democrats Their Strategy for 2020 |url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2018/12/ann-coulter-of-all-people-just-handed-democrats-th.html |website=pastemagazine.com |accessdate=2019-02-16 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217030256/https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2018/12/ann-coulter-of-all-people-just-handed-democrats-th.html |archive-date=2019-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ann Coulter says Jews, like rest of Democratic base, 'hate white men' |url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/ann-coulter-says-jews-like-rest-of-democratic-base-hate-white-men/ |website=www.timesofisrael.com |publisher=The Times of Israel |accessdate=2019-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216151407/https://www.timesofisrael.com/ann-coulter-says-jews-like-rest-of-democratic-base-hate-white-men/ |archive-date=2019-02-16 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Conroy |first1=J. Oliver |title=Ann Coulter believes the left has 'lost its mind'. Should we listen? |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/oct/17/ann-coulter-believes-the-left-has-lost-its-mind-should-we-listen |website=The Guardian |accessdate=2019-02-16 |date=2018-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017203113/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/oct/17/ann-coulter-believes-the-left-has-lost-its-mind-should-we-listen |archive-date=2018-10-17 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[時事評論員|社會和政治評論家]]、畅销书作家、[[專欄作家|專欄作家]]和[[律師|律師]]。

== 生平 ==
她經常出現在各種電視廣播節目，並且經常在公眾和營利場合發表演講。庫爾特出生在紐約的一個保守家庭<ref name=hufpost1>Smolenyak, Megan. {{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/megan-smolenyak-smolenyak/ann-coulters-immigrant-an_b_8332212.html |title=Ann Coulter's Immigrant Ancestors |work=The Huffington Post |accessdate=October 21, 2015 |archive-date=2015-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020190956/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/megan-smolenyak-smolenyak/ann-coulters-immigrant-an_b_8332212.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，曾就讀於康奈爾大學。2010年，她被時代雜誌選為年度百大最具影響力人物之一。

